tooltipCallback.!description:
A callback function that gets a tooltip for a given {@link sap.ui.vtm.SceneNode}. If unspecified, the scene node name is used for the tooltip text.

The first parameter is the {@link sap.ui.vtm.SceneNode} under cursor.<br> The function should return an object containing a tooltip text for the specified scene node. <pre>
  {
    text: [string]
  }
</pre> If function returns null no tooltip will be displayed.
